1.0.name: wordpress/simpleflickr
1.0.description: This is a plugin for Wordpress that allows you to embed a flickr integrated simpleviewer into your Wordpress site. In additional, you are able to specific a path to a standard SimpleViewer XML configuration file to display images from a local gallery.
